  m_text: "We waited outside for what felt like five hours, but in reality it was
    probably only three. That\u2019s when we heard a faint scream. So faint we barely
    heard it, but it definitely came from in the tunnel. None of us wanted to go
    in there so that\u2019s when we called the police.\u201D Now I don\u2019t know
    if you\u2019ve pieced it together yet, but"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0ebd4db9a3aafc541947ecad51ebd5d3, type: 2}
