      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Money. People say that money is the root of all evil. If that is the case,
    Craig is Satan.

    Many describe him as power hungry, conniving and deceitful
    man. Lend me your time and i shall tell you all that we know about this man and
    the wicked life that he lead. Calling him a man is too generous, He was a monster.'
