  m_text: "Then he came back. Out of nowhere. He came back. The neighbour we spoke
    to described it \u201CIt was about nine PM, one day in late April. He looked
    dishevelled, like he\u2019d been through all nine layers of hell, still wearing
    the suit Id always see him in. he walked into his apartment, shut the door and
    didn\u2019t come out for like a month. Near the end of that month "
