  m_text: "Now, this next part is entirely speculation, and you will have to suspend
    your disbelief. From interviews lifted from police reports, a kid, no older than
    18, with a group of friends all around the same age, went to explore the sewer,
    maybe a year later. Taken from the transcript of one of these interviews, \u201CWe
    had dared [REDACTED] to go into the sewer to "
