      m_Calls: []
  m_text: After the last company went under, Craig went mostly off the grid. I say
    that, because we managed to get an exclusive inteview with his neighbour, allowing
    us to learn some of the things that went on. this neighbour said "It always stunk
    of marijuana, and I never really saw him leave." In a police report from that
    time, a quote "Giant Creature" wqs chased out of his apartment and into a nearby
    sewer.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
