  m_text: 'around, and it smelled bad in there so we thought it would be funny to
    fuck with him. So we made him give us his phone, I say made him, but he was willing
    to do it. Anyway, he gave us his phone, and started to go in. Before he got all
    the way in, he complained that it would be dark, so [REDACTED] gave him the lighter
    that he kept in his pocket, and [REDACTED] went in. '
