  m_text: "Where did he go in that year, why did he come back? How did he die? No
    one but him knows. An autopsy was performed on him, but they could not find a
    cause of death. At all. I\u2019m sorry for the rather unfulfilling ending, but
    that\u2019s how it is. Craig is dead. No one got closure. Not the people he harmed,
    not his brother, not you. His funeral was held on the "
