  m_text: I was down on my luck at thatt point, but i didnt want the farm to be flattened
    for industry, so he offered me a deal. I had to get him one millian dollars in
    one month or he would take the farm. And i managed to do it. Just barely. The
    stress i felt in that month was so much more than i had ever fekt in my whole
    life." So, Craig lost out on the farm, lending a hand to his downfall
