      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "I called in a wellness check on him, because I could still hear him moving
    round for most of the month, but in the last week the noises stopped. So I called
    the police. They came, and no one answered the door, so they called the landlord
    and got a key to the apartment. When they went in, a stench so horrible I couldn\u2019t
    even describe it wafted into the hallway, and "
