  m_text: "minutes later they wheeled a body bag out of his apartment. An officer
    came and thanked me for calling, but also informed me that Craig was dead, his
    cause of death unknown.\u201D So, he was dead. The millions of people he affected
    with his money hungry ideals didn\u2019t get any justice."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
